                                        <h2>Getting Started</h2>
                                        <p>Welcome to Bidae! This guide will help you understand how to use Bidae effectively to automate your freelancing bidding process.</p>
                                        
                                        <div class="guide-note">
                                            <p><strong>Note:</strong> Bidae is designed to help freelancers save time by automating the bidding process on freelancing platforms.</p>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <p>To get started with Bidae, follow these steps:</p>
                                        <ol>
                                            <li>Set up your skills and skill sets</li>
                                            <li>Create templates for your proposals</li>
                                            <li>Configure your bidding preferences</li>
                                            <li>Start auto bidding</li>
                                        </ol>
                                        
                                        <p>Let's go through each of these steps in detail.</p>
