                                    <div id="g-skill-include">
                                        <h3>Included Skills</h3>
                                        <p>Included skills are the skills that you want to bid on. Bidae will search for projects that match these skills.</p>
                                        
                                        <p>To add included skills:</p>
                                        <ol>
                                            <li>Go to the Skills page</li>
                                            <li>Enter the skill name in the "Add Included Skill" field</li>
                                            <li>Click the "Add" button</li>
                                        </ol>
                                        
                                        <div class="guide-tip">
                                            <p><strong>Tip:</strong> Add all the skills you're proficient in to increase your chances of finding relevant projects.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div id="g-skill-exclude">
                                        <h3>Excluded Skills</h3>
                                        <p>Excluded skills are the skills that you don't want to bid on. Bidae will filter out projects that contain these skills.</p>
                                        
                                        <p>To add excluded skills:</p>
                                        <ol>
                                            <li>Go to the Skills page</li>
                                            <li>Enter the skill name in the "Add Excluded Skill" field</li>
                                            <li>Click the "Add" button</li>
                                        </ol>
                                        
                                        <div class="guide-warning">
                                            <p><strong>Warning:</strong> Be careful not to exclude skills that might be relevant to your expertise.</p>
                                        </div>
