                                        <h5>How many bids can I place with Bidae?</h5>
                                        <p>The number of bids depends on your subscription plan. Free trial users get 50 bids, while verified users get 500 bids.</p>
                                        
                                        <h5>Can I customize my bid amount?</h5>
                                        <p>Yes, you can customize your bid amount in the Bid Price settings. You can set different bid prices for different project types.</p>
                                        
                                        <h5>How does Bidae select which projects to bid on?</h5>
                                        <p>Bidae selects projects based on your included skills, excluded skills, client stats, budget preferences, and other settings you've configured.</p>
                                        
                                        <h5>Can I stop auto bidding at any time?</h5>
